headline.print_headline: Rosberg Edges Hamilton in Practice for Japanese GP
headline.main: Rosberg Edges Hamilton in Practice for Japanese GP

lead_paragraph: Mercedes driver Nico Rosberg set the fastest time in Friday's opening practice session at the Japanese Grand Prix, edging out teammate and Formula One championship leader Lewis Hamilton.
